    "rationale": "All 13 credibility factors assessed. Although achieved levels fall below required levels across multiple factors, the assessment team determined that the aggregate evidence base is sufficient for the intended regulatory submission context. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification was performed at the COU level and results are considered adequate for a Low assurance level determination. The primary validation result for NIH comparison is considered fit for purpose given the 18.3% MAPE against experimental data.",
